latestIgtvVideos.title: unintentional ASMR Vlog (Delhi to Malshej Ghat)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I don't usually vlog cause I get so consumed by the moment that I forget. This time I tried to. I wanted to add music but felt the  natural sounds were more soothing. This place was truly a treat, so glad work brought me here. Malshej Ghat, Roughly 3 hours away from Mumbai by Car.
